  {underline.bold Usage}
    hygen {bold init} {inverse name} \
      --repo_path {inverse repo_path} \
      --description {inverse description}


  {underline.bold Synopsis}

    {underline name} is the project name, e.g. my-awesome-go-project

    {underline repo_path} is the path to the repo, without the project name, e.g. gitlab.appsflyer.com/rta

    {underline description} is a long project description. e.g. "This is my brand new awesome project!!!"

